{"tid":514060,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"井上尚彌今力爭七度衞冕超蠅量級世界拳王 賽後或告別蠅量級挑戰雛量級","createTime":"2017-12-30T07:39:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-31T13:07:17.000Z","uid":9030,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"dd356ad8baa64c8e3d17b022eadc5dcf069943c2","tid":514060,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T07:39:40.000Z","msg":"「怪物」井上尚彌周六晚就會同29歲法國拳手Yoan Boyeaux交手，力爭七度衞冕WBO超蠅量級世界拳王。井上為咗備戰呢場拳賽，由上個月起就同妻兒分開住，佢就發表勝利宣言：「要攞到成為爸爸後嘅第一勝！」<br />\n<br />\n職業生涯14戰全勝、現年24歲嘅井上早前更加透露，今場係自己最後一次打超蠅量級賽事，暗示下年就會「升呢」挑戰雛量級：「今場可能係我最後一次打WBO超蠅量級世界拳王衞冕戰。不論係身體上抑或心理上，我都覺得自己處於最好嘅狀態，我自信有能力交出好表現，我喺下年會嘗試挑戰第三條世界拳王金腰帶。」"},{"pid":"c5ce1f3689cf1d9db879b6486bdcd43689025a27","tid":514060,"uid":43328,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T07:54:45.000Z","msg":"PR拳王終於等到<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0ae8201f9e2a978d2a472b7635fbae8e4d61eac","tid":514060,"uid":19552,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T08:09:41.000Z","msg":"驚左牙如<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f3ccdaa7e918c0023aa0b02b51503c62454f88a","tid":514060,"uid":28767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e0ae8201f9e2a978d2a472b7635fbae8e4d61eac","tid":514060,"uid":19552,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T08:09:41.000Z","msg":"驚左牙如<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T08:34:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd4d68bfc21efb46249b6567492c30e3eb426988","tid":514060,"uid":54373,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T08:36:52.000Z","msg":"人地升班後<br />\n<br />\n牙如: 好想同佢打"},{"pid":"ffa3ab721fae51366499c0b6a724848e3cfd8387","tid":514060,"uid":36906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T08:36:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"